### Arabic

إِنَّ شَرَّ ٱلدَّوَآبِّ عِندَ ٱللَّهِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ فَهُمْ لَا يُؤْمِنُونَ

### English

Indeed, the worst of all beings in the sight of Allah are those who persist in disbelief, never to have faith—